\n|[[2004\u201305 Scottish Premier League|2004\u201305]]||37||3||4||1||3||0||1||0||45||4\n|-\n|[[2005\u201306 Scottish Premier League|2005\u201306]]||34||1||4||1||1||0||2||0||41||2\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Hibernian Total\n!88!!5!!8!!2!!6!!0!!3!!0!!105!!7\n|-\n|[[2006\u201307 Scottish Premier League|2006\u201307]]||rowspan=\"4\"|[[Celtic F.C.|Celtic]]<ref name=fscfc/>||rowspan=\"4\"|[[Scottish Premier League]]||21||0||2||0||1||0||4||0||28||0\n|-\n|[[2007\u201308 Scottish Premier League|2007\u201308]]||35||1||4||1||2||0||10||0||51||2\n|-\n|[[2008\u201309 Scottish Premier League|2008\u201309]]||36||3||2||1||3||0||6||0||47||4\n|-\n|[[2009\u201310 Scottish Premier League|2009\u201310]]||14||1||0||0||2||0||8||0||24||1\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Celtic Total\n!106!!5!!8!!2!!8!!0!!28!!0!!150!!7\n|-\n! colspan=3 | England\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | [[FA Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | [[Football League Cup|League Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | [[UEFA|Europe]]\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n|[[2009\u201310 Wigan Athletic F.C. season|2009\u201310]]||rowspan=\"6\"|[[Wigan Athletic F.C.|Wigan Athletic]]||rowspan=\"4\"|[[Premier League]]||16||2||1||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||17||2\n|-\n|[[2010\u201311 Wigan Athletic F.C. season|2010\u201311]]||23||0||2||0||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||26||0\n|-\n|[[2011\u201312 Wigan Athletic F.C. season|2011\u201312]]||36||3||1||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||37||3\n|-\n|[[2012\u201313 Wigan Athletic F.C. season|2012\u201313]]||25||1||0||0||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||26||1\n|-\n|[[2013\u201314 Wigan Athletic F.C. season|2013\u201314]]||rowspan=\"2\"|[[Football League Championship|Championship]]||2||0||1||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||3||0\n|-\n|[[2014\u201315 Wigan Athletic F.C. season|2014\u201315]]||0||0||0||0||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|-||0||0\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|Wigan Athletic Total\n!102!!6!!5!!0!!2!!0!!0!!0!!109!!6\n|-\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Career total\n!355||16||23||4||21||0||31||0||430||20\n|}\n\n===International appearances===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! colspan=3